&lt;p&gt;Yateley Community Care Team are looking to recruit a Community Staff Nurse into their dynamic, flexible and forward thinking team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We deliver complex care to people in their own homes and facilitate the best possible care ensuring people are provided with the care they require, where they require it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a team of highly skilled community nurses as well as competent, supportive health care assistants and a associate practitioner.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you would like a new challenge in the Community and aspire to change how nursing is currently delivered then this role may be for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role would suit newly qualified nurses also.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kim Cooper&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kim.cooper9@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
